{
  "id": "RAW_5a37575a",
  "title": "把超算装进口袋，无影在 CES 上给个人 AI 的新答案",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4MTQ4NjQzMw==&mid=2652795337&idx=1&sn=ee4ee906018921faeedb6d46e76c3d56",
  "date": "2026-01-10 12:21:00",
  "author": "智东西",
  "siteName": "智东西",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6117cbcf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibIqicsugh7iaAUT0mNHZMWG86yAcsGgJMgKvY3DYXHmL6Fvd3Oajo67Rg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">桌面感体验，超算级算力。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">作者 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">陈骏达</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 63px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多开发者，可能都有过类似的时刻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型规模越来越大，本地设备开始力不从心。刚跑起来，风扇声就越来越大，显存占用迅速拉满，进度条却像是被按下了暂停键。你很清楚，问题不在模型，而在这台电脑已经到了它的能力边界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.487\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=524873cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibY9zJfhktKcDbjdozdrgr7HPqXT4fydD3QxA7LKRY9wvQr6Lm7JATUw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对个人开发者乃至中小企业而言来说，这几乎是一个绕不开的现实。本地设备性能有限，想尝试稍微大一点的模型就会捉襟见肘。高性能工作站当然存在，但价格和维护成本并不是能够轻松承担的选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">转而使用API，看上去省去了硬件烦恼，却又很快发现模型被包装成固定的接口，某种程度上牺牲了自由度和灵活性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">算力正在成为一种实实在在的生产资料。</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">但问题是，这种生产资料并没有被公平地分配到每一个需要它的人手中。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果对个人或开发者而言，算力不再绑定在某一台具体的机器上，而是像一种随时可以调度的能力，需要的时候就能用上，会不会让很多事情变得不一样？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影亮相CES：</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一台“不像超算的超算”</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">个人开发者对高性能AI算力的需求，正在得到越来越多厂商的正面回应。在年度消费电子大展CES 2026上，桌面AI超算几乎成了所有PC厂商的必答题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中不少方案建立在英伟达DGX Spark平台之上。这些产品的共同思路是，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">尝试把尽可能多的AI算力，塞进一台巴掌大的机器。</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">英伟达和联发科一起为DGX Spark打造了一块超级芯片——GB10，将CPU和GPU封装在一起。在FP4精度下，其AI性能达到1 petaFlop，据说能跑2000亿参数的大模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，这种高集成度是有代价的。DGX Spark的官方</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">售价高达2999-3999美元</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，国内也有销售，128GB+4TB的版本价格来到3万多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/z7ZD1WagSLgUCOH5oXhcl5A2Ics5DBXLekfzGPZAJrM7QfRZnqwRpGibxcrrBcFfoBVV44NibGqzSZI9ohOYMyLw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"450\" data-imgfileid=\"505311678\" data-ratio=\"0.706\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"500\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6fc00c3b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLgUCOH5oXhcl5A2Ics5DBXLekfzGPZAJrM7QfRZnqwRpGibxcrrBcFfoBVV44NibGqzSZI9ohOYMyLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">连续两年亮相CES的阿里云无影云电脑，则给出云厂商对桌面AI超算的回答：一台面向个人消费者的AI超级计算机——</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是一台看起来并不“硬核”的小型终端设备，</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">小到能揣进兜里</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，但正是在这种反差之下，却对应着实打实的高端AI算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3260a81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibYCrtnHvleGVgUg4ToZcYhmCqibuHMIe9Fd6jXbTJ66CibYALjJX5Yvicw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其终端设备叫做“无影魔方”，更像一个算力入口，而不是计算本体。真正的计算发生在云端，通过低延迟连接，把服务器级的AI算力变成一种可以轻松调度的资源，带到现场屏幕上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果把算力比作电力，</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">传统个人电脑更像是每家自备的一台发电机。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">功率和油箱容量在购买时就已经固定，想跑更大的软件，只能换硬件；噪音、散热和维护，也都需要自己承担。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">虚拟桌面则像是接入了一座小型电站。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">你不再维护设备，但能用多少电，取决于为你预留的那台发电机，资源有明确上限。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算背后的算力，</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">更像是一张大型智慧电网。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">终端本身不产生算力，只负责连接。当需求很低时，你可以调用轻量算力；当需要训练模型或进行高强度创作时，可以在短时间内调度更大规模的算力资源。算力随用随取，配置切换无需更换设备，维护和安全也由云端统一完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.685\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aae73679&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcib5n9SbCEbQB2evdOTTgqT58Hicm9yO4sfKQsFJgezLuLMM9sR7hoIfUQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算提供多种算力规格，其中最顶配的版本配备了</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">4块英伟达RTX 5880显卡（单卡48G显存）、96核服务器级CPU和384G内存</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，硬件参数比普通家用电脑高出10倍以上，据说实测综合性能可以达到</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">DGX Spark的4倍</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">价格方面，无影AI云超算提供了按量付费模式，即便是最顶级的配置</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">每小时也仅需2块多</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，而且能实时在各种不同的容量间切换，数据也能同步。我们跟无影的工作人员聊了聊，他们很快就会推出24GB显存的方案，这是许多个人开发者认为有性价比的显存配置。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.594\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=560a7002&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcib9zZpAudiaXc9vJm6cK0nbLWZbU3brQpSLLLIUYWOjRbnypnj5Mv5b7Q%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲无影AI云超算提供多种不同配置</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对应到实际使用中，在顶配的无影AI云超算中，用户可以直接进行模型微调，运行671B参数量的满血DeepSeek，或者完成高强度的AIGC内容生成、渲染和创作任务，而不必再受限于本地显存、功耗和设备成本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">云端算力随叫随到</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“炼丹”到创作都更轻松</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，给AI应用场景配备足够算力，其实只是一个起点。对个人开发者而言，平台是否易于上手和使用，才真正决定了其能否释放创意与科研潜力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多用户对云电脑的最大担忧是延迟和稳定性，例如网络波动可能导致操作不流畅或频繁中断。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">值得一提的是，无影云电脑的技术已经非常成熟。自2020年发布以来，无影已迭代多个产品形态和核心技术，具备</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超低延迟、智能运维和快速恢复</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">等特性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，无影云电脑支持</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">多端接入</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，也就是说，无论是</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">平板、手机</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">还是其他终端，都能直接使用云端强大的算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于非计算机背景的用户来说，环境部署复杂、配置繁琐或依赖安装繁多，也可能成为使用门槛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算针对这些问题提供了一站式解决方案。其内置的</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">镜像市场</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">可以帮助用户快速切换所需开发环境，并提供多版本选择，实现“即开即用”。这样，科研人员、AI爱好者和创作者就可以专注于算法研发和创作本身，而无需为环境搭建和算力调配分心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.533\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad4acb8a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibKxqBytnxodiaWmuBtlVFuUwMicKNgow0XqhiaYhYRoJialictNvibInrnCxA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样一台AI云超算的使用场景，几乎可以覆盖绝大部分AI应用，包括</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">AI绘画、视频渲染、模型推理、Lora训练、论文辅助、代码生成、3D建模</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">等C端高频场景。同时，它还与阿里生态深度集成，能便捷地调用</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">千问大模型、灵构AIGC创作平台</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">等资源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">已经有许多个人创作者和开发者利用无影AI云超算跑通了自己的场景。其中，最热门的用途集中在AIGC领域。在无影内容广场中，汇集了大量与AIGC相关的工作流、镜像等资源，这些内容既有来自阿里官方的版本，也包含了众多AI领域资深创作者的贡献。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.633\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0b8d95b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibxwUaxb7ODqL0NCgEFIRm1Az9uvLDIaHLrLhdRNsbqF8OesZ4IbmgeQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">例如，打开ComfyUI电商智能工作流时，所需环境已预置完成，用户可直接创作或在此基础上进行个性化调整。无影还提供创作加速服务，其DiT加速引擎可嵌入现有工作流，优化扩散模型推理和LoRA微调任务，</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">生成速度提升可达30%以上。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.591\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3153d431&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibSH22GTTmVlMwibwibnJjLNp0IQnyKQ9yo84mHnLLthWncXk7ibicicy3xhw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在使用过程中，用户可根据需求实时切换不同云电脑配置，且实例间的数据可通过无影存储中心实现同步，实现跨实例的文件协同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.587\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e68ddc9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcib8Yv7ociaoic3QlnIRnzVVicX2eAedPPicsEVKogAowbGB1quHTsO9ibJTww%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于开发者来说，他们甚至可以直接用无影AI云超算</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">跑通商业化闭环</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">——在无影上打造的环境和工作流是可以限时分享的，开发者完全可以将自己精心打造的工作流以租用的形式提供给其他用户，从而实现创作变现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了AIGC应用之外，无影AI云超算也能在许多其他场景发挥作用。例如，研究生可以用平板连接无影，</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">跑通原本需要百万级设备才能完成的AI实验</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">；独立游戏开发者可以在家中</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">完成过去需工作室集群渲染的场景</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，并支持按需付费。在搬砖之余，用户甚至可以用无影</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">畅玩3A大作</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，无影已经提供了多款游戏的云游戏服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.505\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=592d6e1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibSIC7MKlCtF9cHMFCXVibquuLwVppoMJ77Qh2TSMc4c4NTcDv2xAXuxQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲CES现场，无影云电脑展示游戏场景的应用</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">个人计算正被重新定义</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent也有了新底座</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算展现了个人计算的新趋势：算力正从少数头部科研机构和大企业专享的稀缺资源，逐渐变得普惠化、随时可得。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过高性能的云端计算，个人用户无需昂贵的硬件投资，就能运行大型AI模型、完成复杂的算法实验，甚至实现视频渲染、3D建模等高算力任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“算力即服务”的模式不仅大幅降低了技术门槛，也显著推动了AI技术在科研、创作和教育等领域的广泛应用。</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">连当前最火的Agent，也能从这一趋势中受益。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在过去，云电脑主要是服务人的计算需求：开发、实验、模型训练等。随着AI技术进化，尤其是具备自主决策、任务执行的Agentic AI出现后，AI本身就会主动发起计算、访问工具、甚至调度其他AI模型，这就对算力底座提出了更高要求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">CES上，阿里云展示了其Agent基础设施产品——</span><strong><span><span leaf=\"\">无影AgentBay</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这是一个给Agent打造的“超级大脑”，能够动态调用云端算力、存储和工具链资源，将复杂任务接入高性能云电脑，突破了Agent在本地设备上的算力限制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.558\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=540ec001&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhFKPeS2nOzqvdrbAtjwIcibJia9GyO4L1LLibQmFWIbFclyH3utIyksv4MwHJcnaTF5eyZTmnCz9aNQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg%26wx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AgentBay集成了云上沙箱环境、算力调度、持久化数据存储和企业级安全等核心功能，还内置了视觉理解、自然语言控制和任务解析等多项AI技术。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其记忆策略可辅助进化，让Agent学会“过目不忘”与“选择性遗忘”，智能管理长期记忆，从容应对复杂、长周期任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于广大Agent开发者而言，无影云电脑的超低延迟、智能运维和快速恢复特性，恰好满足Agent对连续性和可靠性的需求。一站式、即开即用的环境，让开发者无需操心底层部署，直接专注于任务执行和性能优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：云端算力的普惠未来</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI技术的普及仍在不断加速，有越来越多的行业正被AI改变，也有有越来越多的开发者和中小企业，迫切地需要更强大的算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">无影AI云超算代表的模式，给创作、科研、教育和开发等所有依赖算力的场景，提供了一个更为轻量、灵活的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">未来，这种模式的进一步发展，有望推动算力成为像水电一样触手可及的公共产品。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
